\f1\b0 \cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 Flat JSON array of guestbook entries. Capped at 200. Same pattern as artwork_history.json.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ---\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

