\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 ### \cf6 \strokec6 `livedoodle.service`
\f1\b0 \cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 A systemd service unit file that runs the FastAPI server automatically on Pi A boot. Copy to \cf6 \strokec6 `/etc/systemd/system/`\cf4 \strokec4 , then:\cb1 \
\cb3 ```bash\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 \cb3 \strokec11 sudo\cf7 \strokec7  \cf6 \strokec6 systemctl\cf7 \strokec7  \cf6 \strokec6 daemon-reload\cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\cf11 \cb3 \strokec11 sudo\cf7 \strokec7  \cf6 \strokec6 systemctl\cf7 \strokec7  \cf6 \strokec6 enable\cf7 \strokec7  \cf6 \strokec6 livedoodle\cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\cf11 \cb3 \strokec11 sudo\cf7 \strokec7  \cf6 \strokec6 systemctl\cf7 \strokec7  \cf6 \strokec6 start\cf7 \strokec7  \cf6 \strokec6 livedoodle\cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 ```\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 **AI prompt:**
\f1\b0 \cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 "Write a systemd service unit file that runs \cf6 \strokec6 `uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 --proxy-headers`\cf4 \strokec4  as a service, working directory /home/youruser/livedoodle, restarting on failure."\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ---\cb1 \
\
